data.text: @SkyGypsy76 @RyanSeacrest @TheCW @iHeartFestival @fleetwoodmac Fleetwood Mac decided, last minute, they did not want to be aired live. They're dumb.

@SkyGypsy76 @RyanSeacrest @TheCW @iHeartFestival @fleetwoodmac I was wondering why I didn't see them on stage...I turned off the stream 40 minutes ago and just turned it back on...guess I didn't miss Fleetwood Mac after all. 😕
